name: MealJournal
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: meal journal
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Register the meals you ate and the feelings you felt after eating those meals. This way you can have an ally in your journey to a better health. It's like a diary, but with voice. You can forget, but not the Skill. Use if you want to track the connections between the meals and feelings in your routine.
To invoke the skill you can say:
Alexa, open meal journal
You can then try:
Register Entry - Alexa will ask you to say a meal and a feeling. Say it together in the same sentence. For example:
"After eating pasta I felt a headache".
Then you can say:
Consult Journal - So you can hear what did you just register in the Meal Journal.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
